## 9. Refactoring Checklist

**Structure:**
- [ ] Flat module — no `setmetatable`, `__index`, `.new()`, `self:`
- [ ] Standard section order (Config, Controls, Utilities, State, Debug, Functions, Events, Init, Public API, Start)
- [ ] All functions defined in dependency order (callees before callers)

**Debug Logging:**
- [ ] `debugPrint()` implemented with room name prefix
- [ ] Init uses `=== Started ===` / `=== Complete ===` phase markers
- [ ] Discovery logs each component found + final count
- [ ] Registration logs each handler type + count
- [ ] All state changes include source attribution `(Source: ...)`
- [ ] Before → after shown for component assignment changes

**Code Quality:**
- [ ] Early returns for all guard conditions
- [ ] `setProp()` used for all control property assignments
- [ ] `bind()` / `bindArray()` used for all event handlers
- [ ] Control arrays normalized once with `normalizeControlArrays()`
- [ ] Required controls validated in `validateControls()`
- [ ] No single-letter variables except `i`, `k`, `v`
- [ ] 3-letter Q-SYS control prefixes used consistently
- [ ] Event-driven feedback (not timer polling) for component status controls
- [ ] UCI showLayer: base layers (X01, Y01, Z01) excluded from initial hide-all pass

**Metrics:**
- [ ] 50–70% line reduction if refactoring an existing script
- [ ] Script under ~1000 lines
- [ ] Every user interaction visible in debug output
